name: A-1-Small General Service-Non-Time of Use Rate (Single-Phase)
comments: Note: This is not the TOU rate option, so there is a PDP (Peak Day Pricing) of 60 cents/kWh during the PDP events (9 to 15 days out of the year).
description: This schedule is also not available to customers whose meter indicates a maximum demand of 75 kW or greater for three consecutive months.Fixed Monthly Charge is the Total Customer Charge per day, averaged out for a month. ($0.32854 per meter per day * 365 days/ 12 months).
